OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowery rain
OL,6,Fwill clear east at first this evening.
OL,7,FThen clear spells and a few showers
OL,8,Fthrough the evening and overnight.
OL,9,FRather windy around the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FIt will stay largely dry
OL,12,Fwith bright or sunny spells but a few
OL,13,Fshowers possible from the west. Breezy
OL,14,Faround the coast.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMostly
OL,17,Fdry Friday morning, then rain pushes
OL,18,Feast through the afternoon. Bright
OL,19,Fspells and showers on Saturday. Dry
OL,20,Fand bright on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
